o profile ($r \\leqslant r_{\\rm vir}/2$) with halo mass in the range of\n$10^{14}$--$10^{15}\\,{\\rm M}_{\\odot}$, suggesting that this is the major regime\nthat constitutes the cross-correlation signal between weak lensing and tSZ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 16:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-01"}
