actic nuclei. In addition, we estimate the\ndynamical timescales, so called \"trapping timescales\", in the order of a few\nweeks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 16:59:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
