ult of their divergent dynamical histories. This is\nconsistent with the characteristics of the two currently-known interstellar\nobjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 18:00:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-25"}
