its that are largely abundant in FPGAs. This is the key factor that permits\nthe use of affordable hardware with complex deep neural topology and operates\nthem in real-time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 18:09:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 May 2021 15:23:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
