er\nthe full parameter space of CSG binary systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2020 14:16:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 12:26:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
